service: demoexpressjs-lambda

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs18.x
  region: ap-south-1
  memorySize: 256
  timeout: 10
  environment:
    JWT_SECRET: manju123
  iam:
    role:
      statements:
        - Effect: Allow
          Action:
            - dynamodb:Query
            - dynamodb:GetItem
            - dynamodb:PutItem
            - dynamodb:UpdateItem
            - dynamodb:Scan
            - dynamodb:DeleteItem
          Resource:
            - arn:aws:dynamodb:ap-south-1:981625498466:table/*
            - arn:aws:dynamodb:ap-south-1:981625498466:table/*/index/*

functions:
  users:
    handler: handlers/userHandler.handler
    package:
      individually: true
      include:
        - handlers/userHandler.js
        - controllers/userController.js
        - models/dynamoDbUserModel.js
        - routes/userRoutes.js
      exclude:
        - controllers/**
        - models/**
        - routes/**
        - scripts/**
    events:
      - http:
          path: api/auth/{proxy+}
          method: ANY
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: api/auth
          method: ANY
          cors: true

  emergencyContact:
    handler: handlers/emergencyContactHandler.handler
    package:
      individually: true
      include:
